cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.DS, cs.SI, cs.NE 

The paper discusses a modification of the split-LBG classification method for constructing p-adic classifiers in the context of learning. This involves computing clusterings and cluster centers that minimize an energy function. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the following sub-categories: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning)
- cs.IT (Information Theory)
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms)
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks)
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing)
